msgid "RTI"
msgstr "RTI"

#: ../../R/RTI.rst:7
msgid "/R·T·I/, interj\\."
msgstr "/R·T·I/, 間投詞"

#: ../../R/RTI.rst:9
msgid ""
"The mnemonic for the ‘return from interrupt’ instruction on many computers "
"including the 6502 and 6800. The variant RETI is found among Z80 hackers. "
"Equivalent to \"Now, where was I?\" or used to end a conversational "
"digression. See :ref:`pop`\\."
msgstr ""
"6502や6800を含む多くのコンピュータにおける‘return from "
"interrupt’(割り込みからの復帰)命令のニーモニック。変種のRETIはZ80ハッカーの間で見られる。「さて、どこまで話していたかな?」と同等で、話の脱線を終えるために使われる。\\"
" :ref:`pop`\\ を参照。"
